    "4472098": {
      "title": "Glypican-1 identifies cancer exosomes and detects early pancreatic cancer",
      "abstract": "Glypican-1 identifies cancer exosomes and serves as a biomarker for detection of early pancreatic cancer in patients and mouse models of the disease; the findings may enable early and non-invasive identification, and prevention of malignant cancer."
